title: Poochandi Lyrics Masss Song Lyrics
stanzas:
Masss Poochu poochu poo Poochandi Lyrics
Singer(s): Yuvan Shankar Raja & Pooja
Lyrics: Gangai Amaran

pakkam iruppaandi
aettu kadal thaandi.
angirukkum porulayum
adha vittu navuthittu
varuvaan paandi.

avan nalla kaedi
enna venum eduthukko
ippa inga kondu vandhu
tharuvaan di.

onnula palavaatti
adikkura pala lootti.
kannula dagul kaatti
kadhai adikkura
kadha mudikkura
badavaa di.

unakku thaan theriyaatti
onnumey puriyaatti
kanakkuthaan pala kootti
kannu thatti vittu
enni eduppadhu
ivan thaan di.

kanakku pottaa
adhu sariyaachu.
en kadhaikkum adhu
sariyaachu.
adhu eduthu koduthuttu
thaduthu mudikkudhu
potti neyalaachu.

ada irukku illaiyinu
nenaikkaadha.
un nenappa eppozhudhum
koraikkaadha.
adhu maranji kidakkudhu
enakku theriyudhu
adhayum marandhidaadha.

varavu illa selvu
idha kootti kooti
konji kolavu.

Maelogamo, boologamo
engengo pogiren.
mun jenmamo
en jenmammo
yaedhendru paarkiren.
ennangalaal
idhayangalaal
endrun ondraagirom.
vannangalaa
vaasangalaa..

maarudhalai paarthaayaa,
vaerulagam
thondri ponadhey.
naalai marandhu
vaekai marandhu
maayamaai aanadhaey.

kaathu kaathu
avan irundhaandi.
ippa kaiyyil lucku
vara jeichaandi.
